description:
This dataset consist the following contents: 
 1. The data used to generate RSET2 trajectories for monomer, monomer with RNA, dimer and dimer with RNA systems, including initial structures, parameter files and topology files; 
 2. The initial structures for hnRNPA2 FL, hnRNPA2 FL with RNA, hnRNPA2 LCD and hnRNPA2 LCD with RNA systems in phase coexistence simulations;

